的影院已接近300家。近3個月內因營業調整等原因，沒有票房入帳的影院也已多達2100家，占大陸影院總數的1/5。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">分析師與業者感嘆：「電影院產能嚴重過剩，單塊銀幕盈利能力逐步下滑，影院經營困難。這就是大陸電影院線的現實。」</span></span>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-25T12:40:13.000Z","msg":"猶太人...<br />\n唉屌唔撚想打啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lihkg/dog_hb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-25T17:10:14.000Z","msg":"其實未必關事 大陸戲院不嬲作數洗錢<br />\n冇錢洗咪執 好正常"},{"pid":"414cb24e74149a19aaf4a67741e85ad27ce3adbd","tid":916044,"uid":47674,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-25T17:24:54.000Z","msg":"地方政府都冇錢囉<br />\n仲邊有得包場動員組織集體觀看厲害了我的國<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"398d48da353a8786fd22cf6a57be2c815542192b","tid":916044,"uid":57607,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-25T22:36:01.000Z","msg":"戲院唔係用黎洗錢嘅咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n即係依家連錢都冇得洗<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"813841307e9fa0b9dd2e8d8455cc7edcea2031ad","tid":916044,"uid":71655,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-25T22:38:12.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"5ce927ba65c93b6a9c1ef2e868bdff5b8dedeab3","tid":916044,"uid":73340,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-11-25T22:57:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/11/26/065713_18e37a3de0265cee24b054babe638a23.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F11%2F26%2F065713_18e37a3de0265cee24b054babe638a23.png&h=9d6eadb3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n平到咁有咩盈利<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n仲要少人睇"},{"pid":"7f73cc9bb237e556b9a9f49eb74566ec6c4a7cb7","tid":916044,"uid":167879,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-25T23:02:33.000Z","msg":"見好賺個個都開，開到7-11咁<br />\n唔執有鬼"},{"pid":"0def0a34c9f2b5f500c59e84a1e973dba3d09f54",