":"2018-11-25T22:57:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/11/26/065713_18e37a3de0265cee24b054babe638a23.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F11%2F26%2F065713_18e37a3de0265cee24b054babe638a23.png&h=9d6eadb3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n平到咁有咩盈利<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n仲要少人睇"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-26T01:05:57.000Z","msg":"幾年前，係大陸睇戲普遍貴香港20-30%<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ,依家平左咁多？"},{"pid":"576c992c1615ea7aa56aec7125b2c0b822fbaa39","tid":916044,"uid":52881,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-26T01:14:38.000Z","msg":"油站 油站 油站<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"646849976c3422aa190c5ac906fccc5b844cf45d","tid":916044,"uid":44105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-26T01:48:36.000Z","msg":"洗錢呢家野<br />\n你地識條毛咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6f80b15828fc2c66fc8251c0af744389f1d2ee20","tid":916044,"uid":34899,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"137605b062cc800d5695646f7192937284239400","tid":916044,"uid":127988,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"59880a9ca40beb057a86476b7bd5b175a017a6d2","tid":916044,"uid":35814,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-25T23:29:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/11/26/072931_6068365b585f818afe03548c1ee2bb61.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F11%2F26%2F072931_6068365b585f818afe03548c1ee2bb61.gif&h=05bda444&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n出黎打救電影業未？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-11-25T23:31:48.000Z","msg":"香港電影一早被強姦犯大哥毀滅左好耐<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-26T01:50:27.000Z","msg":"邊個強姦犯大哥先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有幾個大哥都係[<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eef4601dcd441ca3e14db4f8f956ba61b4c59e93","tid":916044,"uid":133519,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-26T01:51:31.000Z","msg":"支那人個個都睇老翻, 揾鬼去戲院睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5ba3b65f2be65885597c9e4c40f130682bc37ff2","tid":916044,"uid":18251,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"53e16a5db32d73008f17e2f7ba9af1d28a009968","tid":916044,"uid":35776,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"quote":{"pid":"0155b452566a82a5bc7d6975ef1376f90f3cd003","tid":916044,"uid":67779,"like":39,"dislike":0,"score":39,"quote":{"pid":"a1ffe0f5a3b642a60501b69fc6b6d55d1b806dac","tid":916044,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-25T12:13:48.000Z","msg":"市場飽和 陸電影院爆倒閉潮<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.chinatimes.com/newspapers/20181109000230-260308\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.chinatimes.com%2Fnewspapers%2F20181109000230-260308&d=KzClu49Tl%2B%2BhyQQtCFs%2FdJ7TfgnX9jywtYe9GXZmhCU%3D&h=cfbc73d8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.chinatimes.com/newspapers/20181109000230-260308</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">大陸廣播電影電視總局電影管理局（以下簡稱電影局）資料顯示，截止2018年3月底，大陸電影院計有9965家，銀幕總數54165塊，已是全球第一；最新數據則指出，今年4至10月增加124家，達10089家戲院，但新開的戲院多，倒閉或停業的影院也有近300家，幾乎每天有1家停業，10月甚至有百家影院關門。<br />\n</span><br />\n震撼市場的例子就是曾盛極一時的星美院線，10月頻爆關門、暫停營業等消息，廣東、深圳都有多家星美影城歇業，甚至傳出星美因拖欠員工薪水，維權人數逾3000人。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>戲院太多 稀釋觀眾</strong><br />\n<br />\n針對此一現象，分析師認為大陸電影市場正面臨新一輪洗牌，主因是城市戲院太多，市場幾近飽和；其次，觀影技術升級，形成分眾市場，單塊銀幕盈利嚴重下滑。而房地產市場動盪，影院所在建築已失去投資保值，甚至升值的開發價值，更成為戲院業者「最後一根稻草」。<br />\n<br />\n業者指出，分布在大陸各地的10089家戲院，是指具有一定規模的影院數量統計，市場上還存在大量私人電影院、4D、5D小院線，而這些小電影院也有9萬多家。<br />\n<br />\n但相對來說，戲院蓋得越多，稀釋觀眾的程度就越高，部分縣城還出現嚴重的「供過於求」，造成電影院出現許多沒人看的場次，甚至在大陸年度重要檔期之一的「十一」小長假也一樣。<br />\n<br />\n大陸官方政策促使戲院越開越多，且以一、二線以外城市為主，原本是希望戲院能普及到各個省市、鄉鎮，滿足更多的觀影需求，拉近城鄉之間的差距，但戲院家數及銀幕數成長太快，打破影院與觀影的供需平衡，導致院線的盈利能力遠低於成本支出，結果就是爆出倒閉潮，以及併購風。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>產能過剩 經營困難</strong><br />\n<br />\n據拓普電影智庫數據顯示，今年1至10個月，確認倒閉或停業整改的影院已接近300家。近3個月內因營業調整等原因，沒有票房入帳的影院也已多達2100家，占大陸影院總數的1/5。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">分析師與業者感嘆：「電影院產能嚴重過剩，單塊銀幕盈利能力逐步下滑，影院經營困難。這就是大陸電影院線的現實。」</span></span>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-25T12:40:13.000Z","msg":"猶太人...<br />\n唉屌唔撚想打啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lihkg/dog_hb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-25T17:10:14.000Z","msg":"其實未必關事 大陸戲院不嬲作數洗錢<br />\n冇錢洗咪執 好正常"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-26T01:57:09.000Z","msg":"應該呢個先喺主因<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb429cb780a2c4b9662c20d40f9398a6f0bcd45d","tid":916044,"uid":7903,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-26T02:12:23.000Z","msg":"鼻屎好吃挖到鼻囊出血<br />\n呢個就係支式經營手法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"30274813294427838c00400cd0499b9ac35bc011","tid":916044,"uid":28451,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-26T03:30:09.000Z","msg":"同日本60年代一樣"}]}